### Dynamic Zone 更新測試
### 整體更新 About 的 Blocks Dynamic Zone

@baseUrl = http://localhost:1337
@apiToken = bd8cdd66daecf5db8dbdfbeccbbf4e4adba0a38834f72a66700e31b1ad5864051a3ede3c0f028aae7621ef3077cc2226ed6e61e8c68c80f58d53d70d2ac64f8c401ca0c004378a8d62480ea78190eb9c505571c1b538f659a4a06e8c39e5a1c39ede18dfb600b11511b4f61c84b9fbe92e77a90340122a79e98d8ef9915fb5f1

### 1. 查看目前的 About Blocks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/about?populate=blocks
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}

### 2. 更新整個 Dynamic Zone - 保留現有 Component 並新增
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/about
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "title": "測試標題",
    "blocks": [
      {
        "__component": "shared.quote",
        "title": "更新的標題",
        "body": "更新的內容"
      },
      {
        "__component": "shared.rich-text",
        "content": "這是新增的富文字內容"
      }
    ]
  }
}

### 3. 更新 Dynamic Zone - 只保留一個 Component
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/about
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "blocks": [
      {
        "__component": "shared.quote",
        "title": "唯一的引言",
        "body": "這裡只有一個引言組件"
      }
    ]
  }
}

### 4. 清空 Dynamic Zone
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/about
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "blocks": []
  }
}

### 5. 新增多個不同類型的 Components
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/about
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "title": "完整的關於頁面",
    "blocks": [
      {
        "__component": "shared.quote",
        "title": "引言標題",
        "body": "這是一個引言組件"
      },
      {
        "__component": "shared.rich-text",
        "content": "這是富文字內容組件"
      },
      {
        "__component": "shared.media",
        "file": null
      },
      {
        "__component": "shared.slider",
        "files": []
      }
    ]
  }
}

### 6. 驗證更新結果
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/about?populate=blocks
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}